*   gi_mode (GIMode): Default: 1
*   ignore_occlusion_culling (bool): Default: false
*   lod_bias (float): Default: 1.0
*   material_overlay (Material): Default:
*   material_override (Material): Default:
*   transparency (float): Default: 0.0
*   visibility_range_begin (float): Default: 0.0
*   visibility_range_begin_margin (float): Default: 0.0
*   visibility_range_end (float): Default: 0.0
*   visibility_range_end_margin (float): Default: 0.0
*   visibility_range_fade_mode (VisibilityRangeFadeMode): Default: 0
